iggling itself between the branches of coral. Those trying to harvest coral are occasionally stung by this POK\u00e9MON\u2019s poison barbs if they fail to notice it."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"SEADRA generates whirlpools by spinning its body. The whirlpools are strong enough to swallow even fishing boats. This POK\u00e9MON weakens prey with these currents, then swallows it whole."},{"version":"emerald","text":"The poisonous barbs all over its body are highly valued as ingredients for making traditional herbal medicine. It shows no mercy to anything approaching its nest."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its body bristles with sharp spikes. Carelessly trying to touch it could cause fainting from the spikes."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It is capable of swimming backwards by rapidly flapping its winglike pectoral fins and stout tail."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Its spines provide protection. Its fins and bones are prized as traditional medicine ingredients."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Its spines provide protection. Its fins and bones are prized as traditional medicine ingredients."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Its spines provide protection. Its fins and bones are prized as traditional medicine ingredients."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"An examination of its cells revealed the presence of a gene not found in HORSEA. It became a hot topic."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its fin-tips leak poison. Its fins and bones are highly valued as ingredients in herbal medicine."},{"version":"black","text":"Its spines provide protection. Its fins and bones are prized as traditional medicine ingredients."},{"version":"white","text":"Its spines provide protection. Its fins and bones are prized as traditional medicine ingredients."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Its spines provide protection. Its fins and bones are prized as traditional-medicine ingredients."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Its spines provide protection. Its fins and bones are prized as traditional-medi